HEADWORD: Polypetalous
<hw>Pol`y*pet"al*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets> + <ets>petal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Consisting of, or having, several or many separate petals; <as>as,
a <ex>polypetalous</ex> corolla, flower, or plant</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Martyn.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

